result.description:
Resulting from the stakeholder dialogues in Task 4.5 

The interviews and stakeholder dialogues will be conducted with the purpose of understanding:
	The central value proposition of the Circular Economy Business Model, with specification of products and services;
	The considered values that support the CEBM (profits making logic, traceability, trust, environmental values, social values,);
	Preferences and views regarding the value proposition: does CEBM imply to change established production and consumption patterns? 
	What are the required policy environment requirements as perceived by stakeholders
